<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>个人主页</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background: #f7f7f7;
            color: #222;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .header p {
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 40px;
            height: 2px;
            background: #222;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -5px;
            width: 30px;
            height: 1px;
            background: #999;
        }

        .section p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        ul li::before {
            content: '·';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        .highlight {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #000;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="header">
        <h1>AYU</h1>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Material-driven Design / Sustainability / Sensory Experience</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card section">
        <h2>关于我</h2>
        <p>
            你好，我是 <span class="highlight">wangyiying</span>，一名专注于材料驱动设计与可持续创新的设计师。
            我关注材料的时间性、触觉反馈以及人与物之间的感知关系。
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card section">
        <h2>研究方向</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>材料驱动设计（Material-Driven Design）</li>
            <li>可持续与废弃材料再利用</li>
            <li>触觉与感知设计（Inclusive Design）</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card section">
        <h2>项目</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>可感知湿度变化的纸浆花盆</li>
            <li>甘蔗渣缓冲与吸音材料研究</li>
            <li>面向视障用户的交互型容器设计</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card section">
        <h2>联系方式</h2>
        <p>Email：your@email.com</p>
        <p>Instagram / Behance：your_link</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2026 AYU — Minimal Design Portfolio</p>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
